### Start a conversation
POST http://localhost:8072/api/v1/recommendations/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "user-deec9940-session-1",
  "message": "I just completed a 100 minute gym workout and burned 350 calories. What do you think?"
}

### Follow-up in same conversation (memory retained)
POST http://localhost:8072/api/v1/recommendations/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "user-deec9940-session-1",
  "message": "What specific exercises should I do next time to burn more calories?"
}

### New conversation (fresh memory)
POST http://localhost:8072/api/v1/recommendations/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "user-deec9940-session-1",
  "message": "can you give it in brief"
}
